    <h1>PRO&#xAD;MO&#xAD;TIONS</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200717/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-07-17"><time>2020-07-17</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE | HAPPENINGS</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>Burger King’s XXL-Size Ren­dang Burger</p>
    <p>In cel­e­bra­tion of Sin­ga­pore’s 55th birth­day, Burger King has un­veiled its Ren­dang Burger as its an­nual Taste of Sin­ga­pore. The Ren­dang Dou­ble Beef Burger, fea­tur­ing two beef pat­ties be­tween a 13cm se­same bun, will be avail­able at an ex­tra-large size for the first time from to­mor­row.</p>
    <p>WHERE: All Burger King out­lets</p>
    <p>MRT: Var­i­ous WHEN: Till Aug 31</p>
    <p>PRICE: $9.90 for a value meal INFO: www.face­book.com/Burg­erKingSG</p>
    <p>The Best Of Chef Chan’s Sig­na­tures From Min Jiang</p>
    <p>Min Jiang presents Chef Chan Hwan Kee’s sig­na­ture dishes. An a la carte menu show­cases 10 Can­tonese and Sichuan spe­cial­i­ties that have been pop­u­lar in the past decade, along with new cre­ations. Dishes in­clude stir-fried Iberico pork with duo of onions and hon shimeji mush­rooms, deep-fried sea perch fil­let with spicy ly­chee kumquat sauce and slow-braised African five-head abalone with black truf­fle. Avail­able for take­away and delivery ($15 nett with min­i­mum or­der of $50; free delivery for or­ders of $120 nett and above).</p>
    <p>WHERE: Tu­dor Court­yard, Good­wood Park Ho­tel, 22 Scotts Road MRT: Or­chard WHEN: Till Sept 20, dine-in: 11.30am - 2.30pm (Mon - Sat), 11am - 2.30pm (Sun), 6.30 - 10.30pm daily; pickup & delivery: noon - 3pm, 7 - 10pm</p>
    <p>PRICE: From $14 for a la carte dishes TEL: 6730-1704 INFO: E-mail min_jiang@good­wood­parkho­tel.com or go to good­wood­parkho­tel.od­dle.me/en_SG</p>
    <p>Save-The-Date At Dusk Restau­rant & Bar To Make Up For Lost Time</p>
    <p>En­joy a three-course wine-pair­ing meal with a pre-din­ner cock­tail while soak­ing in sun­set views.</p>
    <p>The Save-The-Date pack­age is ex­clu­sively avail­able for pur­chase on­line and is re­deemable 90 days from the pur­chase date. It comes with a com­pli­men­tary cock­tail shaker, com­pli­men­tary photo to com­mem­o­rate the evening, ro­man­tic ta­ble decor and an F&B voucher.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Dusk Restau­rant & Bar, Level 2 Faber Peak Sin­ga­pore, 109 Mount Faber Road MRT: Har­bourFront</p>
    <p>WHEN: Till Aug 31, 4 - 11pm (Mon - Thu & Sun), 4pm - 2am (Fri & Sat) PRICE: $75++ a per­son</p>
    <p>INFO: www.one­faber­group.com/save-the-date</p>
    <p>Fuller­ton’s Take­away Menu</p>
    <p>Fuller­ton Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore has launched an ex­panded take­away menu fea­tur­ing sig­na­ture spe­cial­i­ties, hearty gourmet boxes, freshly baked breads and sweet treats. High­lights range from Jade’s sig­na­ture sauteed Bos­ton lob­ster with house­made X.O. chilli sauce, served with springy egg noo­dles; to the Asian De­lights gourmet box, which in­cludes items such as kurobuta pork and crab meat ngoh hi­ang; to hand­crafted ar­ti­sanal cock­tails like the Aged Ne­groni. Avail­able for drive-through col­lec­tion at the ho­tel’s drive­way or delivery ($15; free with min­i­mum spend­ing of $100 nett).</p>
    <p>WHERE: The Fuller­ton Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore, Lobby Level, 1 Fuller­ton Square MRT: Raf­fles Place</p>
    <p>WHEN: Pickup & delivery: noon - 2pm,</p>
    <p>6 - 8pm daily PRICE: From $18 nett a dish</p>
    <p>INFO: Or­der at shop.fuller­ton­ho­tels.com/en_SG</p>
    <p>Din Tai Fung Brings Back Old Favourite</p>
    <p>To cel­e­brate Na­tional Day, award- win­ning Tai­wanese eatery Din Tai Fung is bring­ing back its steamed chilli crab and pork xiao long bao for a lim­ited time. The dish is a ren­di­tion of the chain’s fa­mous xiao long bao, filled with suc­cu­lent crab meat and juicy pork in a spicy crab-based broth.</p>
    <p>WHERE: All Din Tai Fung restau­rants</p>
    <p>MRT: Var­i­ous WHEN: Aug 1 - 31 PRICE: $7.50 for four pieces INFO: din­tai­fung.com.sg</p>
    <p>D24 Durian Basque Cheese­cake</p>
    <p>Cre­ated by Or­chard Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore’s pas­try team, this uniquely Sin­ga­porean cheese­cake has a creamy, cus­tard-like in­te­rior filled with D24 durian. Avail­able for dine-in, pickup or delivery via GrabFood.</p>
    <p>WHERE: The Or­chard Cafe, Or­chard Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore, 442 Or­chard Road MRT: Or­chard WHEN: On­go­ing PRICE: $49.30 for a 900g cake</p>
    <p>TEL: What­sApp or call 6739-6565 to book a ta­ble INFO: www.face­book.com/Or­chardCafeS­G</p>


